{"title":"Copy（二）","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":125,"url":"http://www.joyoi.cn/problem/codevs-4337","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html_final","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n题目描述\n<small>Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p style=\"\">在那遥远的dysy有一颓废胖，他在刷oj的时候最喜欢用的算法就是 </p><p style=\"\">  &lt;Ctrl+c&gt; &amp;&amp; &lt;Ctrl+v&gt;</p><p style=\"\">  但是懒惰他只想用 ↑ ↓ ← →来控制光标</p><p style=\"\">  但那只是long long ago了，现在他有了一个新功能键</p><p style=\"\">  这个功能键可以重复前两次的按键，比如依次按下<span style=\"\">↓ ←后按这个功能键的效果就等于<span style=\"\">↓ ←</span></span></p><p style=\"\">  现在光标在（1，1），他想知道把光标移到（n，m）最少需要多少次按键</p><p style=\"\"><span style=\"\">于是他们请作为大犇的你来告诉他答案 =，=</span></p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输入描述\n<small>Input Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>第一行一个整数t，表示t组数据</p><p>2 ~ t+1行每行两个整数：n,m</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n<div  class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n输出描述\n<small>Output Description</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n\n<p>共t行，每行一个整数表示所需最少按键次数</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输入\n<small>Sample Input</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1</p><p>2 2</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n样例输出\n<small>Sample Output</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>2</p>\n\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"panel panel-default\">\n<div class=\"area-title\">\n<span>\n数据范围及提示\n<small>Data Size & Hint</small>\n</span></div>\n<div class=\"panel-body\">\n<p>1 &lt;= t &lt;= 10000</p><p>1 &lt;= n,m &lt;= 10<sup>9</sup></p><p><sup>                      <span style=\"font-family: 'comic sans ms';\">LYL from dysy</span></sup></p>\n</div>\n</div>\n"}]}